---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About MW Brady Law" description="Learn about our experienced legal team and our commitment to serving clients in Frankfort and Crete, Illinois.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About MW Brady Law</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6">
          MW Brady Law has been serving clients in Frankfort, Crete, and the surrounding communities, providing experienced legal counsel in estate planning, real estate, business law, and litigation.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We are committed to providing personalized, professional legal services that protect our clients' interests and help them achieve their goals. Our experienced team takes the time to understand each client's unique situation and provides practical, effective solutions.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Experience</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Our attorneys have extensive experience in estate planning, real estate transactions, business formation and operations, guardianship and probate matters, and civil litigation. We pride ourselves on building long-term relationships with our clients and being their trusted legal advisors.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Community Involvement</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          As members of the Frankfort and Crete communities, we are committed to giving back and supporting local organizations and initiatives that make our communities stronger.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">Contact MW Brady Law today to discuss your legal needs.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
            Contact Us Today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
